{"tid":1980604,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"警長涉警車上掌摑男子 律政司堅持檢控拒以其他方式處理","createTime":"2020-04-20T07:47:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-21T04:02:00.000Z","uid":125168,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"b1e2ef4b9e52a89c72e85acad61126bca38e4eb8","tid":1980604,"uid":125168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T07:47:38.000Z","msg":"當更警長2017年處理一宗襲警案期間涉濫用私刑，在警車上掌摑一名男子，警方調查兩年後起訴警長一項普通襲擊罪。警長早前要求以其他方式處理案件，據了解律政司拒絕，堅持檢控。警長今在九龍城法院否認控罪，繼續保釋候審。<br />\n<br />\n被告黃明偉（47歲）案發時任職警長，被控於2017年4月11日，在土瓜灣道與落山道交界的警車AM7411內襲擊李文瀚。<br />\n<br />\n控方將有5名證人及兩段影片作證，片長共22分鐘，估算需要兩天審訊。辯方確認不會爭議證物連鎖性，換言之不用爭議影片是否真確。裁判官定於7月13日開審，預留兩天。<br />\n<br />\n早前聆訊時，辯方稱有意向控方提出以另類方法處理本案；據最新了解，辯方確曾提出相關要求，但律政司堅持提控。據知案發時被告正處理一宗襲警案，其間涉突然掌摑事主，事主向投訴警察課投訴，警方經兩年調查後拘捕被告。<br />\n<br />\n【案件編號：KCCC2771/19】<br />\n記者 伍嘉豪<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200420/DLS4GPH57A3FDPVMVGKR6TJK4Q/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200420%2FDLS4GPH57A3FDPVMVGKR6TJK4Q%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&d=Sy1M3c%2BVV8kZ1V6TqBoGPnhUmc0vP2awQoWdJLgJf%2FY%3D&h=380f8fb1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200420%2FDLS4GPH57A3FDPVMVGKR6TJK4Q%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&h=b32f02a1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200420/DLS4GPH57A3FDPVMVGKR6TJK4Q/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post</a>"},{"pid":"7b0221d8e7ad5ea57914d45fa8475a327a05d2ac","tid":1980604,"uid":125168,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T07:48:13.000Z","msg":"又係時候上save hk